<div id="corporate-training-home-page">
  <div class="marquee corporate-training-background-image">
    <div id = "marquee" class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="marquee-content clearfix">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <img class="logo corporate-logo" src="<%= asset_path 'corporate_training_logo.png'%>">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h3>Top-notch training for teams in full-stack web development</h3><br>
          </div>
          <p>Our corporate training program certifies your team as full-stack software developers. With a customized curriculum, our experienced educators coach trainees at any level of technical expertise in the skills that apply to your organization’s technology and software, driving efficiency and increasing revenue.</p><br />
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <%= link_to "Schedule Consultation", new_corporate_training_message_path, class: "btn", id: "top-application-button" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- Ends row for Corporate Training Intro" -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="our-program-wrapper page-wrapper">
    <div class="home-section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 our-program">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class = "actualize-logo">Program</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-block col-6-xs phase-border">
              <div class="phase-point-right"></div>
                <h2>Training Philosophy</h2><br>
                <p>At Anyone Can Learn To Code, we are educators who understand how people learn. We bring our classroom to your company, bridging the gap between traditional education and your company’s organizational and revenue goals. Our training produces developers who not only have a full stack of skills, but who can apply their knowledge to your technology and software as well as your clients’.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-block col-6-md">
              <img class="philosophy-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'corporate_training_karen.png'%>">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-block col-6-md phase-border">
              <div class="phase-point-right"></div>
                <h2>Customizable Program</h2><br>
                <p>The ACLTC Corporate Training program is fully customizable based on your team’s needs and goals. We collaborate with you to design an ideal curriculum focused on your organization’s production and revenue goals. We’ll work together to choose the technologies and frameworks raught, a program schedule (including length in weeks and hours in class per day), and deliverables.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-block col-6-md">
              <img class="philosophy-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'corporate_training_ny_trevor.png'%>">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-block col-6-md phase-border">
              <div class="phase-point-right"></div>
                <h2>Outcomes</h2><br>
                <p>After completing our training program, your team of developers will be certified as full-stack developers. They will be proficient in all technologies and frameworks taught throughout the course, familiar with industry best practices, strategies, and methodologies, and able to work efficiently and effectively together to develop excellent products for your organization and for your clients.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-block col-6-md">
              <img class="philosophy-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'corporate_training_terry.png'%>">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- col-12 -->
      </div> <!-- /row -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12-md centered">
          <div class="col-md-12 centered">
            <%= link_to "Schedule Consultation", new_corporate_training_message_path, class: "btn", id: "top-application-button" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> <!-- home-section -->
  </div> <!-- our-program-wrapper close corporate training description-->

