          <br>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
              <div class="skill gray-skill-wrapper border-bottom-yellow">
                <img class="curriculum-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'html_icon.png'%>">
                <h3>HTML</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
              <div class="skill gray-skill-wrapper border-bottom-yellow">
                <img class="curriculum-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'css_icon.png'%>">
                <h3>CSS</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
              <div class="skill gray-skill-wrapper border-bottom-yellow">
                <img class="curriculum-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'mongodb_icon.png'%>"><br />
                <h3>MongoDB</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
              <div class="skill gray-skill-wrapper border-bottom-yellow">
                <img class="curriculum-icon" src="<%= asset_path 'git_icon.png'%>">
                <h3>Git</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <br /><br>
          <p class ="after-word">Our training includes more than instruction. Best practices implemented throughout all modules include Understanding by Design (UbD), Guided Practice, Peer Review, Analysis & Evaluation, Collaboration, and Group & Independent Work.</p><br />
          <br />          
        </div> <!-- col-12 -->
      </div> <!-- row -->
    </div> <!-- home section -->
